  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is comparing two different kinds of splints for patients who have had a surgical
      contracture release of dupuytren's disease. It compares a static splint and a dynamic splint.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
